} Maybe:
} 
}   bindkey -s '^xC' 'cp _!\^ _!$'

or
    bindkey -s 'cpfl' 'cp _!\^ _!$'

Gotta type it fast, though.

Why not e.g.

    cpfl() {
      emulate -L zsh
      local -a last
      last=( ${(z)history[$[HISTCMD-1]]} )
      cp -iv $last[2] $last[-1]
    }

